Description: I am selling my 2006 60th anniversary MIM stratocaster in blizzard pearl. The guitar is in excellent condition with very little use over the last 12 years. I am a lefty and purchased this guitar to have a right handed guitar laying around for friends when they dropped by. Everything works perfectly on the guitar. I especially love the Tex-Mex pickups. The guitar will come with the original paperwork, the trem bar, and a Fender deluxe gigbag. There is a like new hard case partially shown in a couple of the photos. If you (the buyer) would like the hard case instead of the gigbag, I can provide it for an extra $20. Here is the info on the guitar:The Fender 60th Anniversary Standard Strat is for the Fenderfan looking to own a piece of guitar history. This Standard Series Stratfeatures Tex Mex pickups, tastefully engraved neck plate, satin-tinted neck,and eye catching Blizzard Pearl finish to commemorate the diamond Anniversaryof Fender. These were only be available in 2006. This has the 60th anniversarydiamond back plate and the hologram sticker on the back of the headstock. Thestandard models Strats made in 2006 have the hologram stickers but not the 60thanniversary diamond back plate.
